  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Underground_GM_Opening
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - So you followed me down into the Underground. Good. This is the realm of Flesh, where the earth remembers everything that has ever lived.
  - The breath you mastered above will not be enough here. These depths answer to those who understand what endures when life itself is gone.
  - Somewhere in these caverns waits the Guardian of the Underground. Seek it out, and let it judge whether you are ready to carry the Fragment of Flesh.
  - Go. I will be near when it matters.
